# implementation

@impl hive Edit/Write tool POST-success → fireAutoSync(absolutePath) async fire-and-forget
@impl_files_added 2 — auto_sync.ts (core), auto_sync.ts (statusline source)
@impl_files_modified 5 — edit.ts/write.ts (hooks), hive-config.ts (toggle), statusline index.ts/single-line.ts (indicator)
@toggle hive-config sync.auto_sync_after_edit (default on; off/false/0/no disables)
@statusline `⟳ sync(repo) → ubu,ubu2` (during) → `✓ sync(repo) → ubu,ubu2` (1.5s flash) → null
@sentinel /tmp/hive-auto-sync/status.json (statusline reads — separate process IPC)
@rsync_flags --mkpath --inplace (no --delete — single-file safe)
@coupling direct rsync (not via hexa_remote — lower coupling, no bash-interp spawn per edit)

