# net effect on user UX

@before edit on Mac → manual rsync nexus → manual rsync hive → manual rsync hexa-lang → 4-path stdlib deploy → chflags re-lock cycle. 매 edit 5-10 conscious sync 단계.
@after edit anywhere → 100ms 후 ubu1+ubu2 자동 sync → statusline 1.5s 플래시 → audit row. conscious sync 0 단계.

